  101|       |            // https://zips.z.cash/protocol/protocol.pdf#concretesym but fixed to
  102|       |            // 580 bytes in https://zips.z.cash/protocol/protocol.pdf#outputencodingandconsensus
  103|       |            // See [`note::EncryptedNote::zcash_deserialize`].
  104|     58|            enc_ciphertext: note::EncryptedNote::zcash_deserialize(&mut reader)?,
  105|       |            // Type is `Sym.C`, i.e. `𝔹^Y^{\[N\]}`, i.e. arbitrary-sized byte arrays
